TryCatchTrait, TryTrait, Broadcaster, Listener, MessageTransceiver, Repeater, RepeaterMixin, Transceiver, Emptiness, Sized, SpaceLimited, Receiver, Transmitter, Nameable, NamedObject, Mixin, Map<String,Value>
public class CaseFoldingStringMap<Value> extends StringMap<Value>
A StringMap where values that are added with BaseMap.put(Object, Object) are automatically converted to lowercase and can be retrieved with get(Object) in a case-independent manner.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
